This is a small texture map. Hope you like it! 

Features:
Semi-Equal Map (semetric)

Install:

Extract the map file (Install:

Extract the map file (ag_complex_compound_gpk.bsp), and the navigation file (de_dust_mazes.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).


Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: 3-4 Hours

Map Description: This simple based texture map is semetric, therefor quite fair. Great Sniper spots, but also great face-to-face battling. Tunnels for fast, tactical assault.
